import React from 'react'
import {Container ,LeftContainer ,RightConatainer ,ImgBaner ,Text,Desc} from './style'
import brands from '../../Rasim/brands.png'
const Show = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
               <LeftContainer>
                  <Text> Awesome tools for Designer & Developer.</Text>
                  <Desc>Antool is a web collection of information on paid or free Design and Development tools</Desc>
                  
               </LeftContainer>

               <RightConatainer>
                  <ImgBaner src={brands}/>
               </RightConatainer>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Show
